snippet.title: Dorfromantik Demo
snippet.description:
Dorfromantik Demo Walkthrough | no commentary | Gameplay |
Steam Game Festival | February 2021 | Demo
Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLl6FwuqhvIx3IPqMxZfX6yTIF_uEzqLVR
Language Text: English
Language Interface: English
Player: @Tenik 

About this game:
Dorfromantik is a peaceful building strategy and puzzle game where you create a beautiful and ever-growing village landscape by placing tiles. Explore a variety of colorful biomes, discover and unlock new tiles and complete quests to fill your world with life!

Platform: PC
GPU: 2080 TI 
CPU: i9-9900K
RAM: 16 GB
SSD: M.2
